From f89bc2be476216abc6286cff67d89e89a4e4f8b0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: SlayZone Dev <dev@slayzone.local>
Date: Mon, 20 Apr 2026 22:01:22 +0200
Subject: [54/66] slayzone: cap-02 task + project write mojoms and host impls

Add Create/Update/Delete/UpdateStatus/Move methods to TasklistHost and
Create/Update/Delete methods to ProjectsHost, all forwarding to the
sidecar's SQLite-backed handlers. Write methods share a common
TaskWriteResult / ProjectWriteResult envelope carrying ok + error +
freshly-written row. MoveTask is wire-shape-only in cap-02 (sidecar
returns a deferred error until cap-11 adds the ordering column).

Read surface untouched; aggregator snapshots stay as the single source
consumed by region polling.
